items.title: Trump to delay enforcement of TikTok ban with another executive order
items.description: A deal to sell the widely popular platform remains a work in progress.

items.title: 3/31: CBS Mornings Plus
items.description: Widespread storms leave hundreds of thousands without electricity. Also, expert unpacks the $80 million Wisconsin Supreme Court race.

items.title: Dow Jones drops 1,800 points as stock market rout deepens
items.description: Stocks continued to tumble Friday in the U.S. after financial markets suffered their biggest one-day drop since 2020.

items.title: Rat breaks world record for sniffing out wartime landmines
items.description: A mine-sniffing African giant pouched rat named Ronin has been acknowledged by the Guinness World Records.

items.title: Map shows measles cases across U.S.
items.description: CBS News is tracking a outbreak of measles in West Texas that has led to the death of a child, and a growing number of cases around the country.
